name: PhiBrows Brown 2 SUP Pigment 10ml
description: SUP, third generation of World's best pigments for microblading, manual technique. Use in the field of PMU (working with a PMU device) is also possible - to do this, PhiBrows has to be mixed with PhiThinner in order to dilute it. As a mixing tool we recommend PhiMixer.Learn more about SUP pigments here:http:www.phibrows.commicroblading-pigmentsSee more about Honey Effect in our Pigments here:https:www.youtube.comwatch?v=m_G6--lmsP0We are happy to announce that the SUPE generation is coming out soon!
